title: Roopal Tyagi, Kishwer Merchant's cat fight in BB9
text: Roopal Tyagi, Kishwer Merchant's cat fight in BB9 Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) * New Delhi , Oct. 20 (ANI): Claws are out! Audiences recently witnessed the first cat fight of 'Bigg Boss' season nine amongst contestants Roopal Tyagi and Kishwer Merchant.* New Delhi, Oct. 20 (ANI): Claws are out! Audiences recently witnessed the first cat fight of 'Bigg Boss' season nine amongst contestants Roopal Tyagi and Kishwer Merchant. The equation between the two heated up when the 'Sapne Suhane Ladakpan Ke' star blamed Suyyash Rai of always creating a scene during tasks for footage. When Kishwer came to defend her love she got into a cat fight and was heard saying that Roopal cried for footage over her former boyfriend Ankit Gera and got him evicted. (ANI)
